2 types of components
1-stateless Function Component
js k function jo html me retunr krte h wo stateless fucntion components h 
eg -
function Welcome(props) {
	return <h1>Hello, {props.name} </h1>
}


2-stateful class component

regular es6 classes that extend component class from library

they always have render method which return html

